      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA plan must document version control, regression testing, and independent code review consistent with MRL 5 requirements per ASME V&V 40 Table 3.",
      "rationale": "The simulation software lacks a fully documented SQA plan with independent review. Version control is present but regression testing coverage is incomplete. Achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4 for a Class III device at MRL 5."
    },
    {
