      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Standard code verification activities were performed including order-of-accuracy tests on canonical flows. However, hemolysis-specific scalar transport verification was not completed against manufactured solutions. The required level is set at 4 for MRL 5 contexts."
    },
    {
