      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence index computed on three mesh levels. Near-wall resolution in impeller passage is marginal; GCI values exceed 5% in regions of high shear relevant to hemolysis prediction. Required level reflects MRL 5 stringency."
