      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all tested operating points, with uncertainty bounds overlapping at 95% confidence.",
      "rationale": "Predicted hemolysis index values show agreement within 20–30% of experimental measurements at tested conditions. Uncertainty bounds partially overlap experimental data but systematic over-prediction is observed at high rotational speeds."
    },
    {
